                            vestibulum at eros. Curabitur blandit tempus
                            porttitor. Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet
                            fermentum. Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed
                            consectetur.</p>
                            <div class="dropdown-footer">
                                The footer area of the dropdown.
                            </div>
                        </div>                        
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">Members</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <nav class="search">
                <tal:searchbox tal:content="layout.component('bottlecap.search')">
                    Search box
                </tal:searchbox>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="contentWrapper">
        <section class="main">
            <metal:content define-slot="content" />
        </section>
    
        <aside class="column">
            <h3>This is a column.</h3>
            <p>Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum
            nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Morbi leo risus,
            porta ac consectetur ac, vestibulum at eros. Praesent commodo
            cursus magna, vel scelerisque nisl consectetur et. Fusce dapibus,
            tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut
            fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Nullam quis risus eget urna
            mollis ornare vel eu leo. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at
            eget metus.</p>
        </aside>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">Footer with some relevant information.</div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Grab Google CDN's jQuery, with a protocol relative URL; fall back to local if offline -->
    <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script>window.jQuery || document.write('<script src="${layout.bottlecap_static}/jquery-1.6.3.min.js"><\/script>')</script>

    <script type="text/javascript" defer
        src="${layout.bottlecap_static}bottlecap.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript"
        src="${layout.bottlecap_static}dropdown.js"></script>        

    <metal:tailslot metal:define-slot="tail_slot" />

</body>
</html>
</metal:page>
